# PrintShere MVP

P2P 3D printing marketplace. Monolithic **Next.js 14 App Router** + **TypeScript**, deploy target **Vercel**.

## Stack

- UI: Tailwind v3 + Shadcn-style components (`src/components/ui/`)
- State: Zustand (`src/store/`)
- DB: Prisma + Neon PostgreSQL
- Auth: JWT in httpOnly cookie (`src/lib/auth/session.ts`)
- Map: **Leaflet** + CartoDB Positron (no API keys). Do not reintroduce Mapbox.
- 3D: Three.js / R3F — dynamic import, SSR off (`src/components/model/`)

## Layout

- Home `/`: split screen 40/60 — left model upload + price, right map + filters
- Maker signup: `/become-maker` (minimal fields only)
- Maker settings: `/dashboard` (profile, min order price, filaments via +)
- Orders: `/orders` (role-based: customer / maker / admin)

## Roles

`customer` | `maker` | `admin`. Makers have linked `Maker` record via `user.makerId`.

## Maker data model (important)

- Workshop settings on `Maker`: address, lat/lng, pricePerGramCzk, minOrderPriceCzk, printerTypes, status
- Materials are **not** arrays on Maker — use `MakerFilament` rows (material + color per printer type)
- Address is geocoded via Nominatim on signup and profile save (`src/lib/geocoding/nominatim.ts`)

## Env & scripts

- Secrets in `.env.local` (gitignored). Copy from `.env.example`.
- Prisma CLI uses `.env.local` via `dotenv-cli`: `npm run db:migrate`, `db:seed`, `db:studio`
- Test password (seed): `test123456`

## Code style

- Minimize scope; match existing patterns in surrounding files
- Types in `src/types/`, Prisma mappers in `src/lib/*/map-*.ts`
- Prefer extending existing helpers over new abstractions
